    <!-- Color Harmony Explanations (EN) -->
    <string name="color_exp_urban_gothic">Black and grey are the foundation of modern urban style. This combination looks simultaneously strict and stylish.</string>
    <string name="color_exp_soft_fresh">This combination radiates lightness and romance.</string>
    <string name="color_exp_monochrome">Combining several neutral colors is a sign of sophisticated taste and calm confidence.</string>
    <string name="color_exp_analogous">Your colors are neighbors. This creates a smooth transition that looks very expensive and intelligent.</string>
    <string name="color_exp_base_contrast">Using the neutral color (%1$s) allows the bright one (%2$s) to fully reveal itself.</string>
    <string name="color_adv_base_contrast">This is a universal choice for any age. Your look will attract attention thanks to the purity of the color %1$s.</string>
    <string name="color_exp_contrast">This is a combination of opposites. Your look will definitely attract attention and interested glances.</string>
    <string name="color_exp_risky">These colors are in a zone of visual conflict. They may appear "muddy" or too sharp next to each other.</string>
    <string name="color_exp_balanced">These colors create an interesting visual play that emphasizes your individuality.</string>
    <string name="color_exp_triad">A three-color look requires mastery. You have chosen a palette that looks complete and professional.</string>
    <string name="color_exp_creative">You have chosen a bold palette that sets you apart from the crowd. This is the choice of creative personalities.</string>

    <!-- Color Harmony Advice (EN) -->
    <string name="color_adv_urban_gothic">We recommend adding a mesh long-sleeve under a black T-shirt. For the look — an oversized grey coat with black loafers.</string>
    <string name="color_adv_soft_fresh">For the look: a pink dress/polo with white sneakers or a shirt.</string>
    <string name="color_adv_monochrome">Try playing with volumes: wide trousers and a fitted top. Add a quality leather belt or watch.</string>
    <string name="color_adv_risky">• **How to fix:** Try adding white or light grey to create "breathing room" between them.</string>
    <string name="color_adv_creative">To make the look harmonious, choose one dominant color. Let the rest appear in details.</string>
